headline: PARA Q2 Deep Dive: Streaming Progress and Skydance Transition Define Quarter
summary: Multinational media and entertainment corporation Paramount (NASDAQ:PARA) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, but sales were flat year on year at $6.85 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.46 per share was 24.6% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
